{"blogid": "124514783", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "127", "writerCollect": "1165", "writerComment": "167", "writerFan": "849", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "1742", "writerName": "爱你的阿白~", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124514783.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "11640", "writerRankWeekly": "34558", "writerThumb": "328", "writerVisitNum": "185619", "blog_read_count": "4441", "blog_time": "于 2022-04-30 16:33:15 发布", "blog_title": "Tomcat运行框乱码问题解决", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"Tomcat_1\"></a>Tomcat运行框乱码问题解决：</h1>\n<h2><a id=\"_7\"></a>正常的运行框：</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430161241691\" src=\"image\\ec7fa533faa70c2b6e54f238d7c1a24c.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"_11\"></a>乱码的运行框：</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430161357930\" src=\"image\\aab3fa136ae919e04d2c52cb2a282e81.png\"/></p>\n<p>这个是不影响检验tomcat是否安装成功的</p>\n<p>这个是不影响检验tomcat是否安装成功的</p>\n<p>这个是不影响检验tomcat是否安装成功的</p>\n<p>产生乱码的根本原因就是编码和解码不一致<br/> 比较常见的编码格式有Unicode、Ascll码、GBK、UTF-8等等，我们普遍用的都是UTF-8等等。</p>\n<p>这里只需要把UTF-8格式改成GBK格式就好</p>\n<h2><a id=\"_26\"></a>接下来告诉你怎么解决：</h2>\n<p>apache-tomcat-9.0.58-windows-x64\\apache-tomcat-9.0.58\\conf</p>\n<p>打开tomcat文件夹：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430162419640\" src=\"image\\2d5fba344400bde7f88bf35b82dfb7a0.png\"/></p>\n<p>找到conf文件：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430162440232\" src=\"image\\477b8a47039a25c981a1b4410a10afbf.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430162554933\" src=\"image\\1e174887cfd7785a86954be2f9f0ee9f.png\"/></p>\n<p>找到 logging.properties文件：</p>\n<p>用记事本打开文件</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430162818046\" src=\"image\\4033896ad59a8f27a756d37bcf52958a.png\"/></p>\n<p>找到此行代码</p>\n<p>注意是在哪一行</p>\n<p>注意是在哪一行</p>\n<p>注意是在哪一行</p>\n<p>改成：</p>\n<pre><code>java.util.logging.ConsoleHandler.encoding =GBK\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20220430162903317\" src=\"image\\762316c0a8e1851ac00d8c68f95b2bf8.png\"/></p>\n<p>最后记得保存，再次运行，就不会乱码啦</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}